    "In our tests, FNV performed much faster than the default hasher.",
    "These data structures are created by querying the database with Rust.",
    "When the user presses the search button, the queried gene sets are forwarded to the API.",
    "After ensuring that the index is initialized, the code maps the user submitted gene set to a U32 hash set.",
    "It then computes the intersections between the user's gene set and the gene sets in memory and performs the Fisher's exact test using the identified overlap."
